data.description:
Welcome to Your Dream Home in The Oaks at Cane Bay!

Discover the perfect blend of comfort, style, and community in our stunning 5-bedroom, 3-bath residence, boasting an impressive 3,140 sq. ft. of living space. As you step into elegance, the welcoming office space at the entrance sets the stage for a home that's both functional and stylish.

The heart of the home features an open kitchen layout, complete with a custom backsplash that adds a touch of personality. Freshly painted interiors on the main level create a serene and inviting atmosphere that's perfect for both relaxing and entertaining.

Ascend to the private sanctuary upstairs, where all bedrooms are thoughtfully positioned alongside a spacious loft area. This flexible space is ideal for play, study, or simply unwinding at the end of the day.

Community Living Redefined: Nestled in the master-planned community of Cane Bay, this home is more than just a place to live it's a lifestyle. Stroll along numerous walking trails, enjoy peaceful moments by the ponds, or take the poles out and enjoy a day of fishing. Plus, with a golf cart-friendly community , navigating and enjoying the scenic beauty of The Oaks has never been more delightful.

Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your forever home. Experience the perfect combination of luxury living and a vibrant community atmosphere in The Oaks at Cane Bay.

Ready to make your dream home a reality? Contact us today for a private tour.
